about immigration policy,

39:55.351 --> 39:57.644
Ross Fernholm,
a former Arizona State Patrolman,

39:57.729 --> 40:00.522
who now runs the all-volunteer
Independence Border Guards in Yuma,

40:00.690 --> 40:03.275
