and unenforceable aren't laws at all.

42:46.147 --> 42:47.481
- I don't follow.
- Dump out of it.

42:47.565 --> 42:49.107
- And, Mr. McAdoo...
- McAvoy.

42:49.192 --> 42:50.651
- I beg your pardon?
- Doesn't matter.

42:50.735 --> 42:52.569
Why don't we just build a damn wall?

