and you can see it from space.

42:55.448 --> 42:57.074
- Are the Chinese better than us?
- No.

42:57.158 --> 42:58.242
Although there's an old saying,

42:58.326 --> 43:01.036
"Show me a 15-foot wall
and I'll show you a 16-foot ladder."

