43:08.044 --> 43:09.336
The people who build ladders.

43:09.545 --> 43:11.922
- How about we get...
- I'm sorry, okay?

43:12.006 --> 43:14.758
- I'm sorry. Just dump out of it.
- Will, can I jump in?

43:14.842 --> 43:16.593
