- Ugh!

43:18.346 --> 43:20.305
...where pageant contestants
are afraid to speak their minds

43:20.390 --> 43:23.350
when it comes to important
questions and whatnot,

43:23.643 --> 43:25.227
and that's not the America I grew up in.

43:25.311 --> 43:27.562
You're 20 years old.
