43:49.210 --> 43:51.670
Former Alaskan governor
and vice presidential candidate Sarah Palin

43:51.754 --> 43:53.588
weighed in earlier today on Fox News.

43:53.673 --> 43:55.090
Go 907.

43:55.174 --> 43:57.217
Well, then, what the federal government
should have done

43:57.302 --> 44:00.470
was accept the assistance
of foreign countries,

44:00.555 --> 44:03.598
of entrepreneurial Americans
who have had solutions

44:03.683 --> 44:05.183
- that they wanted presented.
- Who?

44:05.268 --> 44:07.936
They can't even get
a phone call returned, Bill.

44:08.062 --> 44:09.396
The Dutch. They are known,

44:09.480 --> 44:12.232
in the Norwegian, they are known for dikes

44:12.317 --> 44:14.985
and for cleaning up water
and for dealing with spills.

44:15.069 --> 44:17.571
They offered to help, and yet, no, they, too,

44:17.739 --> 44:19.948
with the proverbial can't even
get a phone call back.

44:20.825 --> 44:23.493
Okay, what she was saying was that...

44:24.037 --> 44:25.120
All yours.

44:25.204 --> 44:28.206
Yes, okay, the Dutch live in Holland
and Norwegians live in Norway.

44:28.291 --> 44:30.417
That's a mistake that... People make that.

44:30.710 --> 44:35.047
And I think Governor Palin was referring
to an old fairy tale about a boy.

44:35.131 --> 44:37.674
She was saying that people were offering
to help, and that's great,

44:37.759 --> 44:39.593
and phone calls will be returned.

44:48.311 --> 44:50.604
William Duncan McAvoy.

44:51.147 --> 44:54.941
I think your parents wanted to make it
plainly understood that you are Anglo-Saxon.

44:55.193 --> 44:57.611
I came up to personally
apologize for tonight's show.

44:57.737 --> 44:59.112
The show kind of got away from you a little.

44:59.197 --> 45:00.614
It bordered on unprofessional.

45:01.115 --> 45:03.658
Here's unprofessional,
here's the border, and here's professional,

45:03.743 --> 45:05.619
and all the way back here is tonight's show.

