45:51.082 --> 45:53.041
I don't know. I do it all the time.

45:56.295 --> 45:58.547
Get it together down there, fast.

45:59.006 --> 46:01.341
- Got it.
- One more thing.

46:02.552 --> 46:05.137
Your daily private meetings
with Reese are over.

46:05.388 --> 46:07.681
Charlie, I respect you more
than anyone I know,

46:07.765 --> 46:10.016
but I'm the one sitting in that chair.

46:11.602 --> 46:13.019
Yes, you are.

46:16.315 --> 46:20.235
People across America are watching Arizona,

46:20.611 --> 46:23.280
seeing how we implement this law,

46:23.364 --> 46:26.199
ready to jump on even the slightest misstep.

46:26.284 --> 46:29.035
Many opponents
aren't even waiting for that.

46:30.204 --> 46:31.580
You need a drink?

46:33.332 --> 46:34.332
