47:20.338 --> 47:22.214
Palin. How did Palin get into the rundown?

47:23.591 --> 47:25.342
First of all, I'm the EP. Don't slip...

47:25.426 --> 47:27.344
I'm the managing editor
and I don't need your permission...

47:27.428 --> 47:30.055
Yes, you do, and you didn't ask for it
'cause you knew you wouldn't get it.

47:30.640 --> 47:32.724
I made it clear that this show
isn't going to participate

47:32.808 --> 47:35.352
in the endless cycle
of co-dependency between Palin...

47:35.436 --> 47:37.020
- I know.
- And insult to injury.

47:37.104 --> 47:39.564
