48:00.962 --> 48:03.296
to do five minutes
of economic reporting every night.

48:03.381 --> 48:06.299
Victoria's Secret has
a PhD in economics from Duke

48:06.384 --> 48:08.093
and is an adjunct professor at Columbia.

48:08.177 --> 48:09.553
Are you in or are you out?

