of a state where nobody lives on our air.

48:23.401 --> 48:25.819
- I'm don't believe I'm hearing...
- Yes, we fucked up

48:26.279 --> 48:29.406
on a huge subject, but ours was a mistake.

48:29.490 --> 48:30.865
Yours was fear,

48:31.492 --> 48:34.494
a need to be loved by strangers
and not our show.

48:36.455 --> 48:38.039
Be the leader, Will.

48:38.541 --> 48:40.667
Be the moral center of this show.

48:42.503 --> 48:44.170
Be the integrity.

