50:18.099 --> 50:20.558
I want to be a part of what Will and MacKenzie
are trying to do.

50:20.643 --> 50:22.102
Will and MacKenzie are gonna fail.

50:22.269 --> 50:24.771
Jesus Christ, what's...

50:24.855 --> 50:28.108
Just because the scenery fell down
doesn't mean it's not a good play.

50:28.567 --> 50:30.944
Yeah, I don't know what that meant,
but I'm not talking about tonight.

50:31.696 --> 50:33.238
Nobody's gonna watch a classroom.

50:33.322 --> 50:36.616
They'll either be bored or infuriated,
and you will bleed viewers.

50:36.701 --> 50:38.493
And my show with Elliot
will get moved to 8:00.

50:38.577 --> 50:40.495
And at that point, I don't know
that I'll be able to help you.

50:41.163 --> 50:42.580
It was your fault.

50:42.665 --> 50:43.707
Let's break up.

50:43.791 --> 50:45.875
- What did I do now?
- You were too supportive.

50:46.001 --> 50:49.170
- Maggie...
- I feel myself suffocating from your support.

50:49.255 --> 50:50.714
You want truth or support?

50:50.798 --> 50:52.882
Did you think I didn't know I fucked up?

50:52.967 --> 50:54.676
I've been saying it.

50:55.636 --> 50:58.722
I have $45,000 in student loans to pay off,

50:58.806 --> 51:00.515
I spend three weeks' take-home

51:00.599 --> 51:03.059
on half a one-bedroom apartment
the size of a tool shed,

51:03.144 --> 51:05.812
and I'm sitting alone at a bar
with a drink that was made an hour ago.

51:05.896 --> 51:07.772
A good day is
when I have quarters for a dryer.

51:07.857 --> 51:10.066
A bad day is when I blow a newscast.

51:10.151 --> 51:11.568
That's my spectrum.

51:13.571 --> 51:16.614
Support is what I wanted right then.

51:16.866 --> 51:19.159
And I think you're rooting for Will to fail.

51:19.744 --> 51:21.536
You just said it would be
in your best interest...

51:21.620 --> 51:22.620
Listen...

51:22.705 --> 51:24.831
And I know he's not
the cuddliest guy in the world,

51:25.249 --> 51:27.333
but he is trying to do good,

51:27.418 --> 51:29.794
and he's risking a lot to do it,
and you and Reese...

51:29.879 --> 51:32.589
Yeah, yeah. Let's break up.

51:32.965 --> 51:34.591
Don't, no, don't go like this.

51:34.675 --> 51:37.218
I'm sorry. I said the wrong thing.

51:38.512 --> 51:39.721
Don...

51:41.515 --> 51:43.475
Oh, I'm on fire today.

51:46.187 --> 51:48.521
- Evening, Mr. McAvoy.
- Good evening, Manny.

51:50.566 --> 51:52.275
We know how to live with our neighbors here.

51:52.359 --> 51:53.443
What's that?

51:53.527 --> 51:54.569
Your show tonight.

51:55.362 --> 51:56.654
I...

52:37.446 --> 52:38.738
You have to do a shot.

52:38.823 --> 52:40.490
I really only drink when I'm scared.

52:40.574 --> 52:44.744
I would like to have a word with you
right here and right now.

52:50.709 --> 52:51.709
Yes, ma'am.

52:51.794 --> 52:54.754
Don't "Yes, ma'am" me
with your sheepish charm.

52:54.839 --> 52:56.756
Would you like
to go someplace private?

52:56.841 --> 52:58.550
I... You covered for me.

52:58.634 --> 53:00.718
- Don't worry about it.
- I wasn't thanking you.

53:00.803 --> 53:03.513
You and Don,
why do you think I need protecting?

53:03.597 --> 53:05.723
You both like the fantasy of a girl in distress?

53:05.808 --> 53:08.226
- How about I put you in a cab?
- I take the subway.

53:08.310 --> 53:10.687
- Why do you think I need...
- I don't.

53:10.771 --> 53:12.647
But I cover for you, Mac covers for me,

53:12.731 --> 53:14.607
Will covers for everybody,
Charlie covers for Will.

53:14.692 --> 53:16.234
How come nobody's yelling at me?

53:16.402 --> 53:18.152
- You know how bad you screwed up, right?
- Yes.

53:18.237 --> 53:19.404
Is there anyone who feels worse than you do?

53:19.488 --> 53:20.488
No.

53:20.573 --> 53:21.698
Then I doubt it'll ever happen again.

53:24.285 --> 53:25.493
Let me give you money for a cab.

53:25.578 --> 53:28.496
No, I have to go to Don's apartment
and apologize.

53:29.081 --> 53:32.458
- For what?
- For suggesting he would...

53:32.543 --> 53:35.128
You know, for asking...

53:35.546 --> 53:36.921
I'll think of it on the way.

53:37.464 --> 53:40.133
We break up, I apologize, everything's fine.

53:40.426 --> 53:42.093
Sounds like a super-healthy relationship.

53:42.177 --> 53:44.095
- I'd fight for it.
- I will fight for it.

53:44.388 --> 53:46.890
And I'll make it work
through sheer force of will,

53:46.974 --> 53:48.975
just like MacKenzie will with Will,

53:49.059 --> 53:51.436
and just like I made
the immigration segment work.

53:51.520 --> 53:53.730
Will and MacKenzie
are going to kill each other,

53:53.814 --> 53:55.523
and the immigration segment
was a train wreck.

53:55.608 --> 53:57.984
You should shut up more than you do.
Do people tell you that?

53:59.320 --> 54:00.361
No.

54:00.863 --> 54:02.155
You're being polite.

54:05.993 --> 54:07.243
I still don't know why I'm being mean to you.

54:10.497 --> 54:11.706
Tess?

54:12.207 --> 54:14.167
- Would you?
- Yeah.

54:17.171 --> 54:19.881
- Sorry.
- Hang on, all of you.

54:21.675 --> 54:22.967
I'm your senior producer.

54:23.052 --> 54:25.762
Fuck up again like this, I'm gonna get mad.

54:30.476 --> 54:32.518
That's it. Take her to Don's place.

54:39.818 --> 54:42.570
- That was so awesome.
- Thank you.

54:42.655 --> 54:44.072
- Do a shot.
- No.

54:49.536 --> 54:50.828
- Hello?
- Neal, it's Will.

54:50.996 --> 54:53.539
- I hope you don't mind my calling so late.
- No.

54:54.333 --> 54:57.001
I got your number from,
you know, there's a booklet.

54:57.086 --> 54:58.962
- The office directory.
- Yeah.

54:59.046 --> 55:00.463
The guy you found in Spokane,

55:00.547 --> 55:01.839
I want you to get in touch with him

55:01.924 --> 55:03.466
and tell him that you're gonna pay for a cab

55:03.550 --> 55:04.842
to take him to and from work.

55:04.927 --> 55:07.136
He should send you the receipts,
then give them to me.

55:08.430 --> 55:09.472
Will...

55:10.099 --> 55:11.557
Come on, let me post this on your blog.

55:11.725 --> 55:13.184
- No.
- Will...

55:13.268 --> 55:15.812
- Keep my name out of it.
- Yes, sir.

55:16.605 --> 55:17.772
Is MacKenzie around there?

55:19.233 --> 55:20.441
Yeah.

55:20.526 --> 55:22.568
- Can you put her on the phone?
- Sure.

55:28.742 --> 55:30.243
It's Will.

55:36.750 --> 55:39.252
I'm sorry about everything.

55:39.461 --> 55:41.713
I'm just so sorry.

55:41.964 --> 55:43.589
- There's no way I can even...
- I'm in.

55:44.383 --> 55:46.926
- What?
- I'm in. I'll see you on Monday.

55:50.931 --> 55:53.599
- Are you still gonna worry about the ratings?
- Yes.

55:53.684 --> 55:56.436
- Still gonna worry about being popular?
- Yeah.

55:56.520 --> 55:57.979
About being loved by strangers?

55:58.063 --> 56:00.773
Are you gonna keep asking me questions
that all mean the same thing?

56:01.108 --> 56:02.817
Till I get the right answer.

56:04.278 --> 56:05.278
I'm in.

56:07.573 --> 56:08.781
There it is.
